data.description: Captivating Home on Expansive Lot – No HOA! Discover the perfect abode in a desirable neighborhood, free from the constraints of an HOA! This brick ranch boasts 5 bedrooms, with the potential to easily add a closet to one. Set on an impressive 0.69-acre lot, this residence offers a rare opportunity to embrace a spacious lifestyle. Featuring 2 full baths, a generous sun porch, and a detached 2-car garage, this property is brimming with potential. The irrigation system adds a touch of convenience to the expansive outdoor space. Currently occupied by a resident of the neighborhood, this home awaits a new owner ready to undertake some repairs and enhancements. Seize the chance to transform this dwelling into an exceptional residence, tailored to your preferences. Priced with consideration for necessary repairs, this opportunity comes at a value that reflects the potential waiting to be unleashed. Don't miss out – contact your agent today to schedule a private showing. Act swiftly; this attractively priced gem won't be available for long!
